ope, from a perspective that combines insights from the study of religions and education.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aReligion in the public schoolszEngland. 0aReligion in the public schoolszEurope. 0aReligious education of childrenzEngland. 0aReligious education of childrenzEurope. 4aMultikulturalismus. 4aPluralismus. 4aReligionsunterricht. 4aReligionswissenschaft. 7aEDUCATION / Teaching Methods & Materials / Social Science.2bisacsh  aReligious Education, Study of Religions, Religious Plurality, Multicultural Societies.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Social Sciences 2000-2014 (EN)z978311023853208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Theology and Religious Studies 2000 - 2014z9783110638165oZDB-23-GTR08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2007z9783110277135oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PACKAGE ENGLISH LANGUAGES TITLES 2007z978311027719708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET THEOLOGIE/RELIGIONSWISS./JUDAISTIK  2007z9783110277050oZDB-23-DGF0 cprintz978311019661040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311097134740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110971347423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110971347/original  a978-3-11-023853-2  DGBA Backlist Social Sciences 2000-2014 (EN)c2000d2014  a978-3-11-023857-0  DGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1c2000d2014  a978-3-11-027719-7  E-BOOK PACKAGE ENGLISH LANGUAGES TITLES 2007b2007  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SS